<h1>
    
    Welcome to PetRescue. 
</h1>

<p>This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your personal information when you use our website and services. By using our services, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.</p>


<p>
We collect the following types of information:

Personal Information: When you use our website, you may voluntarily provide information such as your name, email address, and location.

Automatically Collected Information: We collect non-personal information such as IP addresses, browser type, and device information through cookies and similar technologies.

Petfinder API Data: Our platform fetches pet listings from the Petfinder API based on user queries but does not store this data beyond user interactions.
</p>
<p>
We use the collected information to:

Provide and improve our pet adoption services.

Personalize your experience by displaying relevant pet listings.

Respond to inquiries and provide customer support.

Maintain the security of our platform.
</p>

<p>

We do not sell or rent your personal information. However, we may share data in the following circumstances:

Service Providers: We may share data with third-party service providers who assist in website functionality.

Legal Requirements: If required by law, we may disclose information in response to legal requests or government authorities.
</p>

<p>

We implement security measures to protect your personal data, but no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure. We encourage users to take precautions when sharing personal details online.

</p>
<p>

Our website may contain links to third-party websites, including Petfinder. We are not responsible for their privacy practices and encourage you to review their policies.

</p>

<p>

Depending on your location, you may have the right to:

Access, update, or delete your personal information.

Opt out of certain data collection practices (e.g., cookies).

Withdraw consent where applicable.

</p>

<p>

We may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with the revised effective date.

</p>



